26 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
27 20-77-408. Medicaid pain relief parity.
28 In establishing and maintaining the formulary and preferred drug list
29 for the Arkansas Medicaid Program, the Department of Human Services shall
30 ensure that a non-opioid drug approved by the United States Food and Drug
31 Administration with no therapeutic equivalent for the treatment or management
32 of pain shall not be disadvantaged or discouraged with respect to coverage
33 relative to any opioid or narcotic drug for the treatment or management of
34 pain on the formulary and preferred drug list, including without limitation:
35 (1) Designating any non-opioid drug as a non-preferred drug if
36 any opioid or narcotic drug is designated as a preferred drug; or
